description: Returns a list of the export jobs for a trained model in a collaboration.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: The collaboration ID of the collaboration that contains the trained model export jobs that you are interested in.

parameters.name: trainedModelArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the trained model that was used to create the export jobs that you are interested in.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token value used to access the next page of results.

nested_items.name: collaborationTrainedModelExportJobs
nested_items.description: The exports jobs that exist for the requested trained model in the requested collaboration.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the trained model export job was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the trained model export job was updated.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the trained model export job.

nested_items.name: outputConfiguration
nested_items.description: Information about the output of the trained model export job.

nested_items.name: members
nested_items.description: The members that will received the exported trained model output.

nested_items.name: accountId
nested_items.description: The account ID of the member who will receive trained model exports.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the trained model.

nested_items.name: statusDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the status of a resource.

nested_items.name: statusCode
nested_items.description: The status code that was returned. The status code is intended for programmatic error handling. Clean Rooms ML will not change the status code for existing error conditions.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The error message that was returned. The message is intended for human consumption and can change at any time. Use the statusCode for programmatic error handling.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the trained model.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The account ID of the member that created the trained model.

nested_items.name: trainedModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the trained model that is being exported.

nested_items.name: membershipIdentifier
nested_items.description: The membership ID of the member that created the trained model export job.

nested_items.name: collaborationIdentifier
nested_items.description: The collaboration ID of the collaboration that contains the trained model export job.
